title: Gambler No. 1
subTitle: Janaki agrees to marry her childhood friend Rummy, but not until he's become rich and powerful, so Rummy decides to become a gambler.

subTitle: A man decides to sell his parent's house after their demise. However, he fails to find a suitable buyer as the house is haunted.

title: Bogan
subTitle: A police officer probes a seasoned robber, oblivious to his hidden power, which allows him to possess people through eye contact.

title: Madhagaja
subTitle: The wife of one of two rival dons sends her son to a distant land to shield him from their relentless feud. However, the son, raised as an orphan, eventually returns to the brutal world of violence.

title: Custody

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

subTitle: A young NRI plans to return to his homeland and marry a woman of his parents' choice. However, confusion ensues after he fall in love with a woman during the course of the journey.

subTitle: When two surgeons mysteriously get murdered by Vetri, a prisoner, the responsibility of locating his accomplice falls on the shoulders of a pathologist.

title: Rider

subTitle: Kathir, an aspiring music director, meets Meera, a musician in a music shop and instantly falls for her. Later, things get absurd when he receives inappropriate pictures of her anonymously.

subTitle: A talented young MMA fighter trains hard to rise up the ranks. However, his goals are hindered when his lover is kidnapped.
